The paper discusses transfer learning, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The use of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN) and zero-shot learning (ZSL) also suggests that the paper may belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The use of knowledge graphs (KG) and their reasoning capability suggests that the paper may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
